301
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:34,880
Look,

302
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,560
this is a covert operation.

303
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,750
Your huge case might give us away.

304
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:39,960
