310
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,040
In your dreams!

311
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:52,590
10 years?

312
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,520
Yes.

313
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,080
Over the years,

314
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:56,710
my sword's been in its scabbard

315
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:58,280
in its case on my back,

316
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,960
nourished by Qi force day and night.

317
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,200
Once it's powerful enough,

318
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:02,470
I'll battle No. 2.

319
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,830
I see. "Ten years it takes to grind a sword.

320
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:06,320
Its frosty edge has yet to be tested."

