00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:25,560
Brilliant!

327
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,440
Spot on! It speaks to me.

328
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,630
What's the next line?

329
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:34,930
Xu...

330
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,200
Qi'an.

331
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,280
Xu Qi'an,

332
00:13:37,350 --> 00:13:38,190
Mr. Xu,

333
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:40,710
what's the next line?

334
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:41,680
Could you tell me?

335
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:42,870
Next line?

336
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:43,870
Yes, there's one,

337
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,110
but I forgot.

338
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,400
Please think again.

339
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,350
I don't remember it.

340
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:52,510
- If I knew, I'd tell you.
- Stop it.

341
00:13:55,470 --> 00:13:56,590
We got company.

342
00:14:13,470 --> 00:14:14,350
Who is this?

343
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:15,190
Go away!

344
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,160
Who are you?

345
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,470
A debt collector.

346
00:15:32,710 --> 00:15:34,030
It's you.

347
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,760
No way!

348
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:39,990
I saw you die with my own eyes!

349
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:43,160
I crawled back from hell

350
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:47,270
to take revenge on you!

351
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,440
