352
00:16:07,230 --> 00:16:09,070
and...

353
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,070
A mummy?

354
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,920
This hand was the evil object in Sangbo.

355
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:59,640
One Chop to Kill All!

356
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,750
(If one chop fails to kill it,)

357
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:14,750
