360
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:59,510
Look up.

361
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:05,120
Jinlian?

362
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,440
Look down.

363
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:16,200
Wow!

364
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,750
They're amazing!

365
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:18,990
That thing is too powerful.

366
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:19,840
It's formidable.

367
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:21,070
We aren't its match.

368
00:19:21,070 --> 00:19:22,230
I've talked to No. 4.

369
00:19:22,230 --> 00:19:24,230
We'll go back to the sect for safety.

370
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:26,750
Wait. You aren't one of the sect members.

371
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:28,160
Why do you have the Jade Mirror?

372
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:31,990
