373
00:19:31,990 --> 00:19:33,070
(I forgot that.)

374
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,360
My brother has to focus on

375
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:36,750
the upcoming Spring Exam.

376
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,230
He let me keep the mirror for now.

377
00:19:43,710 --> 00:19:45,030
- Stop!
- Who are you?

378
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:47,310
It's me!

379
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:48,760
Mr. Xu.

380
00:19:49,630 --> 00:19:51,440
An assassin broke
into Earl Pingyuan's Mansion

381
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:52,400
and killed everyone.

382
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,750
I ran into him while investigating

383
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,310
by His Majesty's order.

384
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:56,990
He's formidable. Don't act rashly.

385
00:19:56,990 --> 00:19:57,920
Alert others now.

386
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:58,760
Yes.

387
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:18,330
Chief,

388
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:19,790
we looked everywhere

389
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:21,790
but didn't find
Earl Pingyuan's lineal son's body.

390
00:20:22,710 --> 00:20:23,920
Tell them to stop.

391
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:36,880
I think

392
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:40,230
other than the killer, someone else was here.

393
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:49,230
Who discovered the massacre first?

394
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:50,470
They did.

395
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,820
- Gold Gong Jin.
- Gold Gong Jin.

396
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,840
When you came,

397
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,880
did you see anyone suspicious in this area?

398
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:59,230
No, sir.

399
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:01,510
Actually, we didn't discover the massacre.

400
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,710
It wasn't you?

401
00:21:03,180 --> 00:21:04,020
Who was it?

402
00:21:04,030 --> 00:21:05,200
Copper Gong Xu Qi'an.

403
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:06,750
Xu Qi'an?

404
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:10,720
Where is he?

405
00:21:10,730 --> 00:21:12,260
(Heng Hui)

406
00:21:14,710 --> 00:21:15,640
Lord Wei,

407
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,470
everyone in Earl Pingyuan's Mansion

408
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:20,360
was killed. No one survived.

409
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:21,600
When were they killed?

410
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:22,840
Who killed them?

411
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,310
Just now,

412
00:21:24,710 --> 00:21:26,510
when I went there for investigation,

413
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,470
I witnessed everything.

414
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:29,680
The killer is a man in a gray robe.

415
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,550
He's above the 4th Rank.

416
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:32,790
I'm no match for him.

417
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,920
I believe he's carrying

418
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,550
the thing once sealed in Sangbo.

419
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:37,840
What makes you say that?

420
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,920
Earl Pingyuan's lineal son

421
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:43,230
died in the same way
as those Imperial Guards.

422
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:47,400
Take a look.

423
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,120
Is he that killer?

424
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:54,580
(Heng Hui)

425
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,720
Yes.

426
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:02,750
He's Heng Hui?

427
00:22:03,230 --> 00:22:05,880
The Azure Hall had
an energy-concealing weapon

428
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,550
that went missing a year ago.

429
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,440
Abbot Panshu of Tianyu

430
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,680
