to not cause himself trouble.

431
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,310
Heng Hui left the Azure Hall

432
00:22:13,470 --> 00:22:15,070
almost at the same time.

433
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:17,680
In that case,

434
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:20,750
Zhou Chixiong did use that weapon

435
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:21,960
to get away.

436
00:22:22,710 --> 00:22:25,680
How did Zhou get Heng Hui's weapon?

437
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:28,640
Heng Hui came back and killed so many people.

438
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,230
I'll track down all of you

439
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,710
and...

440
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:39,750
He's back for revenge.

441
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:41,310
He said he'd continue to kill.

442
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,480
Revenge?

443
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,480
Lord Wei,

444
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:47,960
there might be more

445
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:49,960
to Princess Pingyang's elopement.

446
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,480
Go on.

447
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,400
I found that a year ago,

448
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:57,230
His Majesty meant to
let Duke Yu in the Cabinet.

449
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,510
Meanwhile,

450
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,790
His Majesty fumed.

451
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,960
Officials attacked Duke Yu.

452
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:02,680
Then he passed away in distress.

453
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,750
A year later,

454
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:06,960
Heng Hui came back

455
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:09,070
and killed Earl Pingyuan's lineal son.

456
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,440
The Earl had a group of traffickers,

457
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:13,550
able to send people out of town in secret.

458
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:17,400
Do you mean

459
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:20,990
it's actually a power struggle

460
00:23:20,990 --> 00:23:23,120
between civil officials and the nobility?

461
00:23:25,990 --> 00:23:27,310
Do you know

462
00:23:27,710 --> 00:23:29,200
after Pingyang ran away

463
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,750
and Duke Yu died,

464
00:23:30,990 --> 00:23:33,230
who benefited the most under the table?

465
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,680
You're right.

466
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:40,880
It concerns tons of officials' transfers.

467
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:43,230
Lord Wei,

468
00:23:43,230 --> 00:23:44,680
Earl Pingyuan's Mansion...

469
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:48,870
Jiang Lyuzhong,

470
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:51,070
