473
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,840
I've been digging into them

474
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,120
without alerting any forces or authorities.

475
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:02,920
Since Earl Pingyuan died,

476
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,270
they've been lying low.

477
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:06,160
No one is going after them,

478
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:08,200
so they remain in the capital.

479
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:10,400
I see.

480
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,070
Looks like

481
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:13,960
Earl Pingyuan's lineal son

482
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:16,200
did take over that group.

483
00:24:18,710 --> 00:24:19,960
It's time to crack it.

484
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:20,960
Yes.

485
00:24:22,030 --> 00:24:22,960
You may leave.

486
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,270
I have other things to attend to.

487
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:25,840
Good night, Lord Wei.

488
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:34,640
How dare you steal my case!

489
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,790
Don't be mad, Gold Gong Jiang.

490
00:24:38,710 --> 00:24:41,710
I know you're investigating the Earl's case.

491
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:45,360
It's closely linked to the Sangbo Case.

492
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:48,360
If we work together

493
00:24:48,790 --> 00:24:50,230
to solve them,

494
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:52,310
you'll gain merits, too, right?

495
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,760
Hey,

496
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:58,030
do whatever you see fit.

497
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,200
If you need my help,

498
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,440
just let me know.

499
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:03,710
Thanks a lot.

500
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:05,200
You're welcome.

501
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:07,550
Were you injured?

502
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,070
Heng Hui hit me.

503
00:25:09,070 --> 00:25:10,470
Sorry about that.

504
00:25:16,780 --> 00:25:20,580
(Duke Yu's Mansion)

505
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,860
(Duke Yu's Mansion)

506
00:25:35,860 --> 00:25:38,020
Princess Pingyang might be
involved in the Sangbo Case.

507
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:39,990
That's only my speculation so far.

508
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:50,280
Lin'an.

509
00:25:56,900 --> 00:25:57,900
(Endless Fortune)

510
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:04,750
Ever since the Sangbo Ceremony,

511
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:06,510
Her Ladyship has been bringing you up.

512
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:07,840
You've finally come.

513
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,040
Lin'an.

514
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:32,920
Aunt.

515
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,400
When was the last time

516
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:39,750
