517
00:26:41,230 --> 00:26:42,510
No one eats the pomegranates

518
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:44,200
on the tree.

519
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:47,960
A while ago,

520
00:26:48,470 --> 00:26:49,600
the heavy rain

521
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,920
knocked off many of them.

522
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:56,710
Come in.

523
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:11,680
Aunt,

524
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:12,640
this is...

525
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,680
I have nothing to do.

526
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:20,030
I copy Buddhist sutras

527
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:21,600
to kill time

528
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:24,070
and pray for my husband and daughter.

529
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:29,750
It's been a while since your last visit.

530
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:33,400
Her Ladyship misses you
and Princess Pingyang every day.

531
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,070
Here.

532
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:38,920
Try the newly picked pomegranate.

533
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,550
Is it sweet?

534
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:49,880
When Pingyang

535
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,270
was 10,

536
00:27:53,030 --> 00:27:54,840
her father had the tree

537
00:27:55,230 --> 00:27:57,120
delivered from the South.

538
00:27:59,120 --> 00:28:00,750
She's always been a picky eater.

539
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,960
