542
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:13,680
Are pomegranates on that tree

543
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:16,120
from the South really that sweet?

544
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,390
I think

545
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:21,120
she liked them

546
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,440
simply because she planted

547
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,360
that tree herself.

548
00:28:31,230 --> 00:28:32,550
