556
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:58,900
Then

557
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:01,500
when you hear from her again,

558
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,540
please tell her

559
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:06,340
this year's pomegranates are sweet and juicy,

560
00:29:07,380 --> 00:29:08,820
and let her know...

561
00:29:13,380 --> 00:29:14,860
I'm no longer mad at her.

562
00:29:15,940 --> 00:29:17,500
Were her father alive,

563
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:20,100
he'd forgive her, too.

564
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:22,900
I just

565
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:24,860
want her to come back

566
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,420
to visit me.

567
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:39,820
Uh,

568
00:29:40,940 --> 00:29:42,660
actually, a while ago,

569
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:45,660
I received her letter.

570
00:29:46,780 --> 00:29:48,100
She said she went to...

571
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,500
Zhongzhou.

572
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:53,660
The scenery there was beautiful.

573
00:29:53,780 --> 00:29:54,980
She didn't want to leave.

574
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:56,980
She...

575
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:01,500
